Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, make, python, npm, rust, fzf, fd, ripgrep, neovim
Section: editors
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://www.lunarvim.org/
Description: IDE layer for Neovim with sane defaults
 LunarVim provides a modern, feature-rich Neovim configuration
 with sensible defaults, LSP support, and extensive plugin
 ecosystem – completely free and community driven.
